description: With the Hondo Group mobile app, you have real-time access to your Hondo Group jobs and support ticket status as well as updates and urgent alerts via Notifications.  What's New:  Version 1.0:  System Status Account Information Support for creation and management of online job submissions Location tagging support for flagging your location when you submit your job or request Stay informed in real-time with Push Notifications for confirmation and status changes as your job is worked internally.
